OL,3,CAuthor Wendy Mitchell announces her
OL,4,Cown death in blog post
OL,6,F"Sorry to break the news to you this
OL,7,Fway, but if I hadn't, my inbox would
OL,8,Feventually have been full of emails
OL,9,Fasking if I'm OK, which would have
OL,10,Fbeen hard for my daughters to answer.
OL,11,FIn the end I died simply by deciding
OL,12,Fnot to eat or drink any more."
OL,14,FMitchell, from Walkington, , was
OL,15,Fdiagnosed with early onset dementia
OL,16,Fand Alzheimer's in July 2014, at the
OL,17,Fage of 58.
