OL,4,Cown death in blog post
OL,6,F"I've always been a glass half full
OL,7,Fperson, trying to turn the negatives
OL,8,Fof life around and creating positives,
OL,9,Fbecause that's how I cope. Well, I
OL,10,Fsuppose dementia was the ultimate
OL,11,Fchallenge. Yes, dementia is a bummer,
OL,12,Fbut oh what a life I've had playing
OL,13,Fgames with this adversary of mine to
OL,14,Ftry and stay one step ahead."
