OL,6,FShe added: "Sadly assisted dying isn't
OL,7,Fan option in this country. With
OL,8,Fsomething that will affect 100% of the
OL,9,Fpopulation, regardless of wealth,
OL,10,Fintelligence or ethnicity, it's
OL,11,Famazing how such little value is
OL,12,Fplaced on the act of dying... The only
OL,13,Flegal choice we shouldn't have in life
OL,14,Fis when to be born; for everything
OL,15,Felse, we, as humans, should have a
OL,16,Fchoice; a choice of how we live and a
OL,17,Fchoice of how we die."
